# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore raíz — monorepo .NET (backend) + Node/Vite (frontend)
# Corrige TD-12 (binarios y base de datos versionados)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# === .NET / build artifacts ===
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
.vs/

# === Bases de datos locales (SQLite legado) ===
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.sqlite
*.sqbpro

# === Secretos / configuración local ===
**/appsettings.*.local.json
*.env
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
!.env.example

# === Node / frontend ===
node_modules/
dist/
.vite/
*.tsbuildinfo

# === Logs ===
logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# === Editor / OS ===
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === Docker ===
**/.docker/

# === Test / coverage ===
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
*.coverage
*.trx
